80 Stat. 918","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The words “Federal agency” are substituted for “department, bureau, agency, board, commission, office, independent establishment or instrumentality of the executive branch of the Federal Government” to eliminate unnecessary words and for consistency in the revised chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
